  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "In the spec over here: https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/master/specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md#misc-counters, \r\n\r\nThe block proposer has their `randao layers` incremented every slot when they should only have it incremented in the case where the proposer doesn't propose a block in that particular slot.\r\n```\r\nSet state.validator_registry[get_beacon_proposer_index(state, state.slot)].randao_layers += 1.\r\n```",
